com.lab.model

Class DomainDependentModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lab.model.DomainDependentModel

  • public class DomainDependentModel
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the main class which is responsible for generating the simple version using the domain dependent approach. It performs all the actions as described in the domain-dependent approach section of the document. To perform classification and to get labels, it invokes a web service hosted at python end.
